wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Tuzo IP potto [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|sogllea wikincher adail'lo]] asa.'''

Hi adavni $1 ($2) hannem kelya.
Dil'lem karon zaun asa "$3".

* Adavni suru: $4
* Adavni bond: $5

Tuzo sod'deacho IP potto zaun asa $6.
Upkar korun voir dil'leo soglleo mahiti tujea proxnank zod.

Zor tuka dista hi adavni chukun kelea,  zalear tuka anik mahiti ani nirdesh [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|No open proxies]], vaishvik nitin melltelem.
Na zalear, hea adavne-vixim bhasabhas korunk upkar korun [[m:Steward requests/Global|Meta-Wikicher vinovni kor]].
